Shoutstats

Introduction
~~~~~~~~~~~~
Shoutstats is a fast, free Shoutcast and Icecast server statistic analysis program.
It produces instant and dynamic usage reports in HTML format, for viewing in a
standard browser.

Shoutstats is a bunch of php scripts and a rrdtools database.

It has been written under a Debian GNU/Linux.

That's all for now !

Required
~~~~~~~~
- PHP 4
- rrdtools
- One or more shoutcast and/or icecast servers
- a crontab
- wget

